<div class="title">Experimenting with Wellbutrin</div>
<div class="substance">Bupropion (Wellbutrin) & Amphetamine (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Zooey+Glass&Exact=1">Zooey Glass</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Zooey Glass. "Experimenting with Wellbutrin: An Experience with Bupropion (Wellbutrin) & Amphetamine (Adderall) (exp6908)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. May 18, 2001. erowid.org/exp/6908</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

